HEADWORD: Nanism
<hw>Na"nism</hw> <pr>(n⟦amac⟧"n⟦icr⟧z'm; n⟦acr⟧n"⟦icr⟧z'm)</pr>,
<pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <grk>na^nos</grk> + <ets>-ism</ets>: cf. F.
